item.value: /** * The ProcessFile class handles the processing of text files for simplification * and word replacement based on Google 1000 embeddings and word embeddings. * It uses concurrent processing for efficient execution, modifies the text * based on similarity analysis, and writes the updated text to a file. * * This class relies on the SimplifyingText, Google1000, and WordEmbedding classes * for data sources and provides functionality to update and simplify the text. * * @author Cian Dicker-Hughes * @version 1.0 * @since 1.8 */
